{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_23","type":"agent_message","text":"The backend already exposes both intent parsing and standalone policy evaluation, which is useful here because explicit commands can be normalized into the same action batch without pretending to be natural-language AI output. I’m reading those request/response models now to decide whether the shared command mapping should live purely in the client or be centralized and reused on both sides."}}
